SELECT
    "site",
    "subsite",
    "obsidianTot"
FROM public.wide_format_data
WHERE "obsidianTot" IS NOT NULL AND "obsidianTot" > 0
ORDER BY "obsidianTot" DESC;

SELECT
    SUM("obsidianBlades") AS total_obsidian_blades
FROM public.wide_format_data
WHERE "unit" = 'N1W4' AND "collectionYear" = 64;
